Texts.Chs: 探索德尔塔·弗雷亚 II

Texts.Eng: Lifting up this book has triggered ^red;strange visions^reset; of a place covered in snow and ice, and coordinates to that place. I should enter the coordinates for ^orange;Delta Freya II^reset; into my SAIL. It calls to me. I am compelled to obey.

Texts.Chs: 无法用语言来表达疯狂和怪异根植在我的灵魂深处。我的一部分永远地消失在了那个地狱里。
Texts.Eng: There are no words to express the madness and strangeness that tugs now at the very roots of my soul. A piece of myself has been forever lost to that hellish place.
